{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "Bulk Data Exfiltration — api.soledrop.co (HIGH)" }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*A single source is bulk-pulling data from the SoleDrop API — high sensitive-endpoint volume and/or oversized responses.*\n\n*Source IP:* `{{local_var.src_ip}}`  (geo: {{virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.country}})\n*VirusTotal:* {{virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious}} engines malicious\n*AbuseIPDB:* {{abuseipdb-check-ip.body.data.abuseConfidenceScore}}/100 abuse confidence\n*Sensitive-endpoint pulls (/export /download /customers /billing /models):* *{{get-dv-events.body.data[0].sensitive_hits}}*\n*Distinct API paths enumerated:* {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].distinct_paths}}\n*Largest response:* {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].max_bytes}} bytes on `{{get-dv-events.body.data[0].largest_uri}}`\n*ATT&CK:* T1567 / T1030" }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Before you block:* confirm `{{local_var.src_ip}}` is not an authorized bulk export / ETL pipeline or backup job run by a service account — legitimate data movement also produces large pulls. If it is sanctioned, Dismiss." }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Alert:* <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>" }
    },
    {
      "type": "actions",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "Block at Cloudflare" },
          "style": "primary",
          "value": "approved"
        },
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "Dismiss — False Positive" },
          "style": "danger",
          "value": "dismissed"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": "`{{local_var.src_ip}}` was blocked at the Cloudflare edge (IP Access Rule) by {{wait-for-slack.body.user.username}}. Alert: <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}

{
  "data": { "text": "Analyst {{wait-for-slack.body.user.username}} APPROVED Cloudflare block of {{local_var.src_ip}}. Evidence: {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].sensitive_hits}} sensitive-endpoint pulls across {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].distinct_paths}} distinct paths on api.soledrop.co, max response {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].max_bytes}} bytes, largest {{get-dv-events.body.data[0].largest_uri}}; VirusTotal malicious={{virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious}}, AbuseIPDB={{abuseipdb-check-ip.body.data.abuseConfidenceScore}}. Playbook: OneFlare Golden Data-Exfil Response." },
  "filter": { "ids": [ "{{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}" ] }
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": "Dismissed as false positive (e.g. shared corporate egress / NAT). No block applied. Alert: <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}

{
  "data": { "text": "Analyst {{wait-for-slack.body.user.username}} DISMISSED as false positive. No Cloudflare block applied. Rationale: assessed benign (likely an authorized bulk export / ETL or backup job by a service account). src_ip {{local_var.src_ip}}; VirusTotal malicious={{virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious}}. Playbook: OneFlare Golden Data-Exfil Response." },
  "filter": { "ids": [ "{{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}" ] }
}
